      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how beautiful this ride is\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car smell! I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
