      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 power plant with a fully serviced dual-VANOS system and valve clearances recently shimmed to factory specifications. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original structural integrity. The 6-speed Getrag transmission is paired with a fresh clutch and a tight limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque transfer. The suspension remains true to its original geometry with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for neutralized body roll. The exterior retains its factory paint depth, while the interior shows zero compression or wear on the Nappa leather bolsters. This is a mechanically sorted, thermally-cycled-with-care specimen for the discerning collector.",
