      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous inspection. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, resulting in a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or blemishes. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and the cabin retains its original showroom scent. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, featuring a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively at authorized service centers. It recently underwent a comprehensive multi-point inspection and received a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, low-mileage example with a clean title and a complete folder of service receipts. It drives tight, smooth, and exactly as intended by the manufacturer.",
